                            <div id="maincol-inner">
			      
			                          	  <div class="region region-home-content-about">
    <div class="content">
        <p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><strong><abbr title="Software Paradigms International Group, LLC">SPI</abbr></strong>, founded in 1994, is an award winning IT services and solutions provider for retailers around the globe. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"></span></p>
<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/io6mGGXYKZQ" width="560"></iframe><p></p>
<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:18px;"><strong><abbr title="Software Paradigms International Group, LLC">SPI</abbr></strong></span> is transforming <strong>RETAIL</strong> from <strong><em>Silos</em></strong> to <span style="font-size:18px;"><strong>Omni-Channel</strong> </span>with services, products, and solutions.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><strong>IT Services</strong></span></p>
<ul><li><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><a href="https://www.spi.com/prime-digital-retail">Prime Digital Retail</a></span></li>
<li><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><a href="https://www.spi.com/enterprise-application-integration">Enterprise Application Integration</a></span></li>
<li><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><a href="https://www.spi.com/warehouse-management-services">Warehouse Management Services</a></span></li>
<li><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><a href="https://www.spi.com/spi-quality-assurance-and-testing">QA &amp; Testing</a></span></li>
<li><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><a href="https://www.spi.com/spi-infrastructure">Infrastructure Solutions</a></span></li>
</ul><p><br /></p>
<p><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><strong>Retail Products &amp; Solutions</strong></span></p>
<ul><li><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><a href="http://www.spi.com/spi-buyer"><abbr title="Software Paradigms International Group, LLC">SPI</abbr> Buyer</a></span></li>
